column9:
More emphasis on the enterprise applications of these technologies. My dad works in mainframe development, and I feel like a lot of students don't realize that this type of thing is the backbone of most banks. Don't force feed them into a career in IT, but make them aware of their presence at the large firms many of us would like to work at.

I'd like to see more about data mining as well.
